raw_text = "# SPDX-FileCopyrightText: The Threadbare Authors
# SPDX-License-Identifier: MPL-2.0
~ start
With all their preparation, the test wasn't quite so scary. Their friend's help certainly made a difference.
Despite all of Nora's earlier doubts, their test came back with an A grade and none of the dreaded red marks!
Nora realized that when they took time to ground themselves and share their struggles with a trusted support system, they could overcome any obstacle in their way.
Let's go back to Fray's End so you can return this woven A grade to the Eternal Loom...
=> END
"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
